column3: Look, Avere! All these people have come to make you a gift of their souls! Isn't that kind of them?
Even <hex:022C0DFF07><hex:022903EB0203><hex:FF02> <hex:0203> is here! Now your dream of becoming like <hex:02080DE905FF04>her<hex:FF04>him<hex:03> can come true!
What...what have you done? Aveeerrreee! Noooooo!
